# Android Release Readiness

- App must be prepared for Android APK/AAB.
- Configure app icon, splash, package name, permissions, and version.
- Avoid unnecessary permissions.
- No background location.
- No realtime GPS.
- EAS Build instructions must be documented.
- Preview builds should support APK for customer demos.
- Production builds should support AAB for Play Store readiness.

